b to remember his movie characters ' names ? ) would be 20 years old since she was 5 when that happened and not only is she married to someone who looks 30ish but also has a kid who looks around 7 and 10 ! Did she get around during middle school ? And also why would Pantyhose be after Annie ? What connection does she even have with the characters of the original movie ? And a BIG HUGE MOVIE MISTAKE I found in this movie is that when the doctor is writing in his notebook does anyone notice that he 's just SCRIBBLING ? Wow , how professional , Doc ! So , what is the explanation for all of the questions I asked above ? IT 'S A POINTLESS MOVIE WITH NO THOUGHT PUT INTO IT AT ALL ! I will try to find a copy of the original movie that comes with just that movie and that 's it ( Maybe a couple of extra features , any Special Edition of it yet ? ) . Then I will return this DVD and hopefully this review and all the others will prevent those who have n't seen it from seeing it thus making movie stores get rid of it and this movie may not exist anymore ! Please let that be so ! Sorry this review is so long . I 'm just angry at this movie I had to vent somehow
