e day as this , and despite being a rather flawed film itself , really comes out a masterpiece compared to this.<br /><br />So in the end , this is not a film so bad it 's good , or so bad it 's in any way enjoyable , even drunk . It 's just a mess , and worth no - one 's time watching .
